+/// CR 118.9: Mana-cost-alternative-grant static — "You may [pay X] rather than
+/// pay [the/its/this <object>'s] mana cost for [filter] spells you cast."
+/// Rooftop Storm / Fist of Suns / Jodah class. `scan_contains` is a cheap
